Pastor Penuel Mnguni of the End Times Disciples Ministries in Soshanguve, Pretoria, visited TB Joshua s Synagogue Church of all Nations in Nigeria on Sunday and explained why he had fed his congregants live snakes.Narrating his story to Prophet TB Joshua, snake Pastor revealed shocking details, &#8221; I was an Agent of Devil , my mission was to recruit people into the Devil&#8217;s Kingdom, i initiated more than 50 000 people, i am tired of worshiping the devil, Deliver me man of God&#8221;,he shouted.NB: Some sensitive parts of his confession were pulled out